There are opinions regarding a possible vaccination obligation in the future.
As of January, it must be settled by insurance and optional.
For example, Nahlas Rudolf Kalovsk<0xC3><0xBD>, the president of the association, said that mandatory vaccination would be more positive.
Its association has long promoted vaccination against pneumococcal disease.
