I think this is a direction that must now be followed, said Kalovsk<0xC3><0xBD>.
But the Ministry of Health does not want to change the process of vaccination against pneumococcal disease.
We are not considering it at all at the moment, said its spokesman Vlastimil Sr<0xC5><0xA1>e<0xC5><0x88>.
