I liked what he said, said Ms. Palin, right-wing hegemon of the Republican Party, to the USA Today newspaper, adding that she herself had addressed the theme of war "sometimes necessary" in her memoirs that have just been published.
War is, of course, the last thing I think Americans want to do, but it is necessary.
